Astro::Montenbruck

Library of astronomical calculations, based on "Astronomy On The Personal Computer"
by O.Montenbruck and T.Phleger, Fourth Edition, Springer-Verlag, 2000.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command from the parent directory of the library:

   perldoc Astro::Montenbruck

You can also generate local HTML documentation with

  perl script/createdocs.pl

Documentation files will be installed to docs directory.

